The dataset contains 20,000 images of people. For each person, a first impression of them was created. The first impression is a text consisting of several sentences.

# 💴 For Commercial Usage: To discuss your requirements, learn about the price and buy the dataset, leave a request on **[TrainingData](https://trainingdata.pro/datasets?utm_source=kaggle&utm_medium=cpc&utm_campaign=impressive-dataset)** to buy the dataset
